MONDAKOTA GAS COMPANY, a corporation, Appellant, v. Collins G. REED, and Mrs. Collins G. Reed, his wife, if any, et al., Appellees. No. 20402. United States Court of Appeals Ninth Circuit. Aug. 1, 1966. Daryl E. Engebregson, James J. Palm-ersheim, Billings, Mont., for appellant. Crowley, Kilbourne, Haughey, Hanson & Gallagher, Billings, Mont., for appel-lees.

Before HAMLEY and JERTBERG, Circuit Judges, and THOMPSON, District Judge.

PER CURIAM:

The judgment and orders under review on this appeal are, and each of them is, affirmed for the reasons stated in the opinion of the district court reported in 244 F.Supp. 327.
